channel.title: Any pre eoc website guides (Mainly for armor and weapon stats)
channel.description: I have trouble finding any websites with pre eoc data for items and what not. I am hoping with 07scape there is enough need for a website that one may be around, or am I wrong and sol?

item.title: Any pre eoc website guides (Mainly for armor and weapon stats)
item.dc:creator: @Ykcud Ykcud
item.description:
@Ykcud wrote:

[quote=“Stu, post:4, topic:511032”][quote author=Ykcud link=topic=629276.msg4270106#msg4270106 date=1364456161]

I don’t plan to make a website if that is what you are asking
[/quote]y aer yuo not fndi owen websiet?

If I understood your question correctly, its because I have already looked for quite some time for a website with pre eoc data. I am hoping someone else has had better luck that I do.

Also, if you can help it, could you please use correct spelling?

Don’t mind him he’s a loveing idiot who is using a bad meme.
I’ve used this ever since 2007 came out, this should be what you’re looking for.
http://web.archive.org/web/20070617120834/http://runehq.com/[/quote]

Thank you! I was well aware of the site but didn’t check if it ever had old stats on it for some reason.
